sequenceDiagram
  participant Student as Virtual Lab
  participant GQL as GraphQL
  participant Events as Lab Events
  participant Kafka
  participant Analytics as Analytics Ingest
  participant PG as Postgres
  participant WS as WebSocket

  Student->>GQL: recordProgress step 5
  GQL->>Events: Save event
  Events->>PG: lab_events table
  Events->>Kafka: Stream event
  Kafka->>Analytics: Consume
  Analytics->>PG: fact_progress
  Events->>WS: Live update
  WS-->>Student: Real-time feedback
